## 动态表单列表（增删行）

```vue
<div v-for="(item, index) in form.items" :key="item.uid" class="dynamic-row">
  <el-form-item
    :label="index === 0 ? '规格' : ''"
    :prop="`items.${index}.name`"
    :rules="itemNameRules"
  >
    <el-input v-model="item.name" placeholder="请输入" />
    <el-button type="primary" link @click="handleRemoveItem(index)">删除</el-button>
  </el-form-item>
</div>
<el-button type="primary" link @click="handleAddItem">+ 添加一行</el-button>
```

```ts
let uid = 0
const createItem = () => ({ uid: ++uid, name: '' })

const handleAddItem = () => {
  form.items.push(createItem())
}

const handleRemoveItem = (index: number) => {
  form.items.splice(index, 1)
}
```

- 每行需稳定 `key`（勿用 index 作 key）
- 提交前过滤空行（若业务允许）

